        {
            "title": "人行：首9個月房地產貸款餘額跌0.1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article_content line_1_5em\">\n<div id=\"upper\"><p><font my=\"my\" style='-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);border-width:0px;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:\"Microsoft JhengHei\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-break:break-word;word-spacing:0px;'>人民銀行表示，截至9月底，房地產貸款餘額52.83萬億元，按年跌0.1%，首三季減少840億元。</font></p></div>\n<div id=\"lower\"><div class=\"articlelogin\">\n<p><font my=\"my\" style='-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);border-width:0px;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:\"Microsoft JhengHei\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-break:break-word;word-spacing:0px;'>人行指，房地產貸款表現基本平穩，截至9月底，房地產開發貸款餘額13.61萬億元，按年跌1.3%，首三季則增加925億元。個人住房貸款餘額37.44萬億元，按年跌0.3%，首三季減少2411億元。</font></p><p><font my=\"my\" style='-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);border-width:0px;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:\"Microsoft JhengHei\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-break:break-word;word-spacing:0px;'>住戶消費貸款則保持增長，截至9月底，不包括個人住房貸款的消費性貸款餘額按年升4.2%。企業、事業單位貸款增長較為平穩，工業中長期貸款、普惠小微貸款均有較快增長。</font></p><p><font my=\"my\" style='-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);border-width:0px;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:\"Microsoft JhengHei\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;outline:0px;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-break:break-word;word-spacing:0px;'>人民幣各項貸款餘額270.4萬億元人民幣，按年增長6.6%。</font></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><h2><br/> </h2> </div></div>\n</div>",
